# Bluemap-x-TysFixes
A Minecraft resource pack designed to help Bluemap detect or add missing models/textures for core Minecraft.

This repo will undergoe dramatic changes once Bluemap 5.0 is release as all these assets will be built in.
[See notes here.](https://github.com/BlueMap-Minecraft/BlueMap/pull/536)
If you still need this pack it will be available under the 4.x branch.
